entries.femaleVariant: We're in our room.
All set.
Where's the shaft?
Neutralize him. Use the Flathead to jack into him.
Didn't pick it for snazz. Offers quickest access to the dweller and servers.
Dweller's inside.
Just as planned.
Dweller won't realize somethin's up?
Could drive a tank through here and he wouldn't feel a breeze. Dead to the world, that one.
[Take chip] Here goes nothin'.
Here goes.
Why me? Why do I gotta slot it in?
Why's it gotta be me?
Unlike someone, I haven't run up my tab with Vik. Got last-gen firmware, low flow.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="chica" b="Just do it, " a=", ain't got all day."/>

entries.femaleVariant: Sounds simple enough.
What now?
Penthouse security is neutralized.
Flathead ready?
Flathead prepped to go?
<mothertongue l="mex" m="chica" b="Almost there, " a="."/>
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Mierda." b="" a=" Little gonk's stuck."/>
Just gonna stand there and look at it? Gonna have to switch to manual control.
Here.
Patching you through to in-cam view. Might get a little disoriented, but don't freak.
What makes you think it was for you?
He addressed it to the kind housekeeper who finds him. Note inside said "Sorry for the mess."
Think he's single?
A week – that's all we can promise you.
We will try. And that is all I can promise you.
'Kay…
Shaft may link both rooms, looks like.
Huh...? What the hell--?
You can't just go locking people out of their homes, places of work…
Arasaka will cover the cost of any and all penalties assessed.
This isn't about the money. It's election season. How d'ya think this'll make me look?
People'll start saying I've lost control of Watson – district I'm from!
Looks like he's havin' trouble.
Shit...
OK, he's at it.
Now toggle over to the other cam.
Shit – think he mighta noticed that!
Hold, I'll use their internal comms.
Grrugh... What now?
Now, V.
You know – good-lookin', filthy-rich, has that naughty look in his eye. He's stayin' in the penthouse.
Mean Yorinobu Arasaka? Men like him're always single.
Got a winner.
Good. Jackie, how's the Flathead lookin'?
Boot up your scanner, look around.
Systems're operational, charge at a hundred…
Simplicity's sometimes toughest to master.
There was blood everywhere, but at least he left a tip.
Am I the only one that just gets puke and used condoms?
I'd give him a ride and wipe him out…
Honey... stick to wipin' that glass, huh? You're leavin' streaks everywhere!
Dweller's just beyond the door.
Gotta be another way. Lemme think...
Let's figure it out.
Sit tight. Wait it out.
Eightieth floor?! Seriously?!
What do we do now?
I'll flash-freeze him with a daemon... Old lingo, don't ask…
Gotta jack straight into his chair. He won't know what hit him, then.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Perfecto." b="" a=" Let's start the show."/>
Lemme neutralize him.
Flathead oughta be able to neutralize him.
Good thinking. Lemme graft a demonoid onto your link.
And ya know ya gotta jack the Flathead directly into his chair, right?
Make it sound like I'm new at this.
OK, sent. He's all yours.
OK, got a clear view.
Let's do this. Steer him outta the shaft.
All set. T?
Get him to the next vent.
OK, Flathead's in.
Patching you into next cam now.
And? See anything?
Yep.
Do your thing.
Uhhh, Bug? Got a hitch.
What now?
Housekeeping's in my way.
Gotta distract her. Hmm, let's see what's on the subnet...
All right, on it.
Uhh... Kat? Something's up with the tank…
Jesus Christ -- you got any idea how much those things cost?!
Hey, Bug! It worked!
Psh, ain't seen nothin' yet.
Mighta found our way in!
Bingo.
Got the port.
Flathead, jack it in, we'll have eyes on the next room.
OK, have the Flathead jack in.
Got another cam here.
Can't breach it. You gotta jack the Flathead into the CCTV subnet.
Look around – CCTV access port's gotta be around there.
Wanna use it? You'll need to connect the Flathead to the CCTV port.
Second cam, maybe? Could see something.
Look for the CCTV port. See anything?
Jack the Flathead in, next cam's ours.
Won't get anywhere without that next cam. Flathead into the CCTV subnet, jack it in now.
Send the Flathead over there, then toggle over to the second cam.
Don't know yet.
Could always swap between cams…
Flathead into the chair, V, jack in.
V, take the control shard from Jackie. Gonna link your Kiroshis to surveillance so you can guide the bot.
Bug? How're you doin' on time?
You there, Bug?
Soooo listen, ICE is thicker than I thought. Piercing it'll take a couple hours.
A couple hours?! Can't do it any faster?
Want my brain to burst into flames?
And we are back in biz.
Got another cam other side of the door, but it's disabled.
Yeah. Look around for a CCTV port.
You'll have to get the Flathead in there first, though.
Weren't you supposed to look for the shaft?
Still nothin'? C'mon, can't be that hard.
Whoop! Got him! Love those daemons!
[Stand]
Surveillance cover the whole hotel?
Surveillance cover the whole hotel?
Mhm. Even the bedrooms in the suites.
Guests don't care?
You'd be surprised what people're willin' to give up to feel secure.
Aurelius? Aristotle? Who's it this time?
Yours truly, that one's mine.
Pretty snazzy. Too bad we ain't stayin' the night. Nice choice, Bug.
Lucky for us, Yorinobu's an exception. Penthouse is dark, no hotel security.
To keep an eye on the dweller, yeah.
What did you do?
Called him upstairs, urgent business. Some poor psycho's threatening to jump.
Flathead can jimmy the lock.
Want me to enable?
Still weird the hotel's only got one 'runner.
Decent dweller's as good as a dozen rank-and-file.
Flathead stays, right?
Punching into Konpeki's main net. You go ahead and log out.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="¡Así es cómo se hace!" t="That's how it's done!" b="" a=""/>
How ya feelin'?
Fine. Little dizzy, that's all.
Take a few deep breaths, all right?
Yeah, yeah, I'm here.
Just siddown and enjoy your snazzy suite.
Where's the damn justice in it?
Now you fire up the Flathead and find the shaft entrance.
<kiroshi l="mex" o="Sí, sí, me acuerdo." t="Yeah, yeah. I remember." b="" a=""/>
Can't see a thing from where I'm poised in the subnet. Need a scan of the room, V.
Keep movin', no time for back-pattin'.
Whaddaya think? Why'd he give it all up?
Hmm? Who gave what up?
Yorinobu Arasaka. The good life, I mean.
Old news, I know. Just got to thinkin's all.
Did the same with the Valentinos, didn't you?
It's like, think... You got everything, right? Eddies, education. Your pops can snap his fingers and turn half the fuckin' planet into a nuclear wasteland…
You can kick the rat outta the corp, but…
Maybe he wanted to ditch the system.
Rich asshole's whim – why should I care?
Ehh, fuck 'im! Why do I need to care about some bougie prick and his street-kid fantasies?
But instead you're like, "Nah, fuck it," and whaddaya go do?
Heheh, musta been a hoot, huh? "I'm Yorinobu Arasaka. Would you folks like to join my gang?" Tsh... poser with corp protection.
Heheh, and the name, too! Steel fuckin' Dragons?
Hah, oh man. A wannabe gangoon's wet dream.
Got bored of bein' rich, then got bored of playin' tough.
entries.maleVariant: Got bored of bein' rich, an' then got bored of playin' tough.

entries.femaleVariant: Tough to ditch the system when the system's your own family.
Said it yourself – you can kick the rat outta the corp...
Black sheep's still a sheep, eh?
One way to put it.
But you'll never kick the corp outta the rat.
Prolly just got bored – all one percenters do sooner or later.
Went down the same road, didn't you?
Hooked up with the Valentinos, spewed some lead, then walked away.
Ey! That ain't the same thing!
You ghost from your fam, chip some RealSkinn and play gang leader for a few years. For what?!
Thanks, I will! V, you take it easy, OK? Rest up a bit.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="hijo de puta" b="Don't be puttin' me on a level with that " a="."/>
Hey, Bug... were, uh... were you on comms that whole time?
Three and a half hours.
Eehh... about that stick up the ass…
Mean the one up mine?
Ehh, slip of the tongue, y'know…
I know.
Now's your chance to make up to me.
Fuckin' tourist.
Tourist or not, he just walked into the lobby.
Maybe he just wanted outta the system.
So then why'd he come back?
Crawled back on all fours, tail between his legs, fuckin' cheap-ass rebel…
Start a fuckin' gang! Steel Dragons or some shit!
And I paid a price for it too, 'member? Three slugs to the chest – feels like one's still in my left lung…
Heywood's not some fuckin' palace in Japan. I didn't have no choices.
Might wear expensive suits, but he's a biker at heart, always itchin' for a ride…
Who?

Got a smartroom panel. Useful?
What would you say to a TV?
Holoprojector, maybe?
Terrarium's got a control panel.
Terrarium's got a temp and air quality controller.
I'd say, "Keep lookin'."
Nope.
Hm, no, not in the least.
Somehow I doubt it.
[Lower temperature]
[Enter shaft]
Smartoom panel?
How about the TV?
Holoprojector?
Got a terrarium.
Terrarium's temp control?
Preem, yeah. Sic the Flathead on it.

[Send Flathead]
[Open]
[Jack in Flathead]
[Open]
We gonna stand here at attention? C'mon, take it.
<mothertongue l="mex" m="Híjole" b="" a=", V... It's just a chip, not a live grenade."/>
